{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"404dff3ea8","title":"对新疆党政军机关三反斗争情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"961231b403","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"404dff3ea8"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e84f82ab3e","name":"王震","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"3886f96986","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。"},{"id":"46083ae0c2","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王震，当时任中共中央新疆分局书记、中国人民解放军新疆军区代司令员兼代政治委员。"},{"id":"fc9540868f","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王震1952年3月1日关于新疆党政军三反情况给毛泽东并军委总政的报告说，在新疆省级机关和军队中，三反已接近基本上解决问题的阶段。鉴于新疆有复杂的民族问题和起义军队等问题的特殊情况，对军委直属队及二、六两军，二十二兵团，第五军和本地民族干部三反斗争中的问题，拟分别不同情况在政策上区别对待。报告第二条是对二十二兵团三反斗争中的一些问题的处理意见。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cb679274c2","type":"title","text":"对新疆党政军机关三反斗争情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8"},{"id":"3886f96986","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周阅后，转王震阅","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8"},{"id":"46083ae0c2","type":"paragraph","text":"此报告中（二）条（2）（3）两项似太严，还要宽一点。究竟如何才怡当，请周研究后找王震一谈。其他各条办法都好","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8"},{"id":"fc9540868f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8"},{"id":"0ca80b4079","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"404dff3ea8"}],"page":{"id":"ab7889b015","publ